sourcesContent: function t(){return t=>t.addInitializer((t=>new e(t)))}class e{constructor(t){this.host=t,this.host.addController(this)}hostUpdated(){void 0!==this.host.selectable&&null!==this.host.selectable?this.host.ariaMultiSelectable="multi"===this.host.selectable?"true":"false":this.host.ariaMultiSelectable=null}}export{e as AriaMultiSelectableController,t as ariaMultiSelectable};
